Package: resolve
Title: Species Composition Based Prediction Using Neural Networks
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Gilles", "Colling", , email = "gilles.colling051@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Predict plot-level environmental attributes from species composition
    using multi-task neural networks. Combines feature hashing for species names
    with learned taxonomic embeddings. Built on a C++ core using libtorch for
    GPU-accelerated training and inference.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.0
Depends: R (>= 4.0.0)
Imports:
    Rcpp (>= 1.0.0),
    R6,
    methods
LinkingTo:
    Rcpp
SystemRequirements: C++17, libtorch (PyTorch C++ API)
URL: https://github.com/gcol33/RESOLVE
BugReports: https://github.com/gcol33/RESOLVE/issues
